## DB reachability
Compose has no postgres service. `rtk pg_isready -h host.docker.internal -p 5432 -U postgres -d ggn_scyllax` returned:
host.docker.internal:5432 - no response
Host-local verification `pg_isready -h localhost -p 5432 -U postgres -d ggn_scyllax` returned:
localhost:5432 - accepting connections
`psql -h localhost -p 5432 -U postgres -d ggn_scyllax -c 'SELECT 1 AS reachable;'` returned:
 reachable
-----------
         1
(1 row)
## verdict
reachability: ok
Local Postgres is reachable on localhost:5432 for database ggn_scyllax. Compose stack and sales service are running. Compose does not define postgres; host.docker.internal:5432 specifically returned no response, while localhost:5432 accepted connections and SELECT 1 succeeded.
